name: The Gentlemens Supply Co
tag_list: curated, shopping, ecommerce, startup, tech, fashion, clothing
overview:
Curated Shopping for men - convenience without commitment. We are a tech based startup with a combination of bricks and mortar (via Claude Sebastian - with over 60 years experience - www.claudesebastian.com.au) and online (the entire system has taken a year to build) with design, stylists and integrated intelligent backend systems - to form this better way for men to shop - www.gentlemenssupply.com We aim to increase the style aptitude of the modern gentleman.

your style Build your own profile. Curate your crate with the help of our expert style consultants.

your terms Try garments on at your convenience. There are no upfront payments. Shipping and returns are also free.

it’s yours Keep and pay only for the items you love. Send the rest back within 14 days.
